In [54]:
net.blobs['data'].reshape(1,        # batch size
                          1,         # single-channel 
                          800, 800)  # image size
transformer = caffe.io.Transformer({'data': net.blobs['data'].data.shape})

#For RED
image_red = caffe.io.resize(image[:,:,0], (800,800))
transformed_image=[]
transformed_image = transformer.preprocess('data', image_red)
net.blobs['data'].data[...] = transformed_image
pred = net.forward()
plt.subplot(3,2,1)
plt.imshow(pred['prob'][0][0])
plt.title("Input_Red_Output_Channel_1")
plt.subplot(3,2,2)
plt.imshow(pred['prob'][0][1])
plt.title("Input_Red_Output_Channel_2")

#For GREEN
image_gr = caffe.io.resize(image[:,:,1], (800,800))
transformed_image=[]
transformed_image = transformer.preprocess('data', image_gr)
net.blobs['data'].data[...] = transformed_image
pred = net.forward()
plt.subplot(3,2,3)
plt.imshow(pred['prob'][0][0])
plt.title("Input_Green_Output_Channel_1")
plt.subplot(3,2,4)
plt.imshow(pred['prob'][0][1])
plt.title("Input_Green_Output_Channel_2")
